{"tid":2255925,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國將受理BNO居留簽證申請   中國外交部：英國歪曲《中英聯合聲明》","createTime":"2020-10-24T03:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T04:09:23.000Z","uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4bc6a2dcb6f244f7ed07e32285d6c1935e571d","tid":2255925,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:20:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/4563947/2020-10-23/news-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86BNO%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B+%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%93%8D%E5%BC%84/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F4563947%2F2020-10-23%2Fnews-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2590%2586BNO%25E5%25B1%2585%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%2B%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%25BC%2584%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vJFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=584a5f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/4563947/2020-10-23/news-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86BNO%E5%B1%85%E7%95%99%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B+%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E4%BF%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%93%8D%E5%BC%84/?variant=zh-hk</a><br />\n<br />\n英國政府公布英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）居留簽證計劃詳情，持BNO港人及其近親明年1月31日起可申請特別簽證留英。外交部駐港公署表示，強烈不滿和堅決反對，要求英方立即糾正錯誤，停止偽善表演和政治操弄。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署發言人表示，在香港回歸前，中英曾就BNO護照問題互換備忘錄，英方在備忘錄中明確承諾，不給予持有BNO護照的香港中國公民居留權。發言人指，英方為有關人員在英居留和入籍提供路徑，公然違背自身承諾，粗暴干涉中國內政和香港事務，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。發言人又指，英方賊喊捉賊、栽贓抹黑，歪曲《中英聯合聲明》，又強調《中英聯合聲明》沒有一個字、一個條款賦予英國在香港回歸後對香港承擔任何責任，英方對回歸後的香港無主權、無治權、無監督權，英方所謂「對香港人許下的承諾」完全是一廂情願、無稽之談。"},{"pid":"1f0096857ce0d9d59d8f043d3c94c38ea73b1642","tid":2255925,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FDE8g9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FDE8g9.gif&h=43af0eea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"440031b410808000beab4017db7b354c95cba3a9","tid":2255925,"uid":18381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"支那：  外交部發言人陸慷今日在外交部例行記者會上表示，《中英聯合聲明》作為一個歷史文件， 不再具有任何現實意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5959dce6485137061f6f4e159acfad2251479e99","tid":2255925,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"講到明係聲明<br />\n<br />\n即係兩邊各有各講，成份野無共識alignment基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f7009301b6a1b00213e0d358f72a2e39e6d918","tid":2255925,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"支持口交部推出反制措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n准許所有英國市民<br />\n係1月31日開始申請CNO VISA<br />\n5 + 1 移民大灣區及取得大灣區户籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1045a58669194dfa179490010223cbee690e94a2","tid":2255925,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"BNO不嬲只要住夠英國特定年期就可以入籍轉BC架啦 <br />\n而且英國一向都有大把渠道俾BNO申請各類英國居留簽證 <br />\n依家只不過提供多一個方法俾佢地去儲夠轉BC果個居留年期要求 做乜班外交賤狼好似發現新大陸咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d38680be8c8b2e96d0635ff68e55b549bdb5f7b","tid":2255925,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"